comments: Holiday (DAL) steps forward into Olynyk's (UTA) space and initiates body contact during his upward shooting motion, affecting his jump shot attempt.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Dunn (UTA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Dunn (UTA) extends his arm as he contests and makes illegal contact with Irving's (DAL) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Irving (DAL) quickly slides his arm off of Markkanen's (UTA) body and marginal contact occurs as they engage and disengage off-ball before the screen is set.
Olynyk (UTA) continues to shuffle to his left and deliver contact to Kleber (DAL) which affects his ability to defend.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) deliver body contact that dislodges Markkanen (UTA) from his rebounding position, affecting his ability to pursue the loose ball.
Holiday (DAL) moves alongside Agbaji's (UTA) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Irving (DAL) keeps his hand on the side of the ball and avoids placing part of his hand underneath the ball during the drive.
Irving (DAL) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes more than two steps before shooting.
Holiday (DAL) swipes down and avoids making contact with Horton-Tucker's (UTA) during his upward shooting motion on his driving shot attempt.
Holiday (DAL) slightly extends his arm and marginal arm contact occurs with Horton-Tucker (UTA) as rips through at the start of the drive.
Correctly called 24 second violation on Irving (DAL).
Holiday (DAL) commits a take foul on Horton-Tucker (UTA).
Horton-Tucker's (UTA) free throw does not make contact with the rim.  Possession is correctly awarded to Dallas.
Dunn (UTA) commits a take foul on Irving (DAL).
